:: Talk to Rob {"position":"2050,825","size":"100,100"}
You decide to talk to Rob.

After listening to your concern, he leans back in his chair and starts to think.

''Rob: ''"Hmmmmmm, we'll first of all thanks for bringing this to my attention."

''Rob:'' "Our device is used to record a patient's heartbeat. They don't send electric shocks like an implantable cardioverter defibrillator (ICD) or inject drugs like an insulin pump."

''Rob:'' "Our device sends data through short range wireless signals, so any malicious party would have to be close to our clients. That's more of a physical attack rather than a remote hack over the internet. It's not exactly something that can be pulled off easily en masse."

Quietly Rob whispers to you. 

\
''Rob:'' "And even if this eventually leads to a client's data being leaked, well we've been selling 'anonymized' data already so it's already out there."

(if: (history:) does not contain "Talk to Bob")[
    ''Rob: ''"Maybe Bob would know more."
]
